@page "/faq"

@using Kohinoorea.Client.Services
@inject HttpClient Http
@inject ILocalStorageService LocalStorage

<PageTitle>Faq</PageTitle>

<main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="eyebrow">Common questions</div>
        <h1>Answers buyers usually need before they <span class="gradient-text">start</span></h1>
        <p>This page combines the product FAQ, common support questions, and the refund policy summary from your brief.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container faq-grid">
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is Kohinoor EA?</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA is a premium automated trading system developed for MetaTrader 4. It is designed to analyze market conditions, execute trades based on predefined logic, and manage positions with a disciplined algorithmic approach.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Does it work on MT4?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Kohinoor EA is built specifically for the MetaTrader 4 platform and integrates smoothly with MT4-compatible broker accounts.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Which pair does it support?</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA is optimized for XAUUSD (Gold), one of the most actively traded instruments in the market. It is designed to work with the dynamic nature of gold price movements.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is it fully automated?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Once installed and configured, Kohinoor EA can monitor the market, place trades, and manage open positions automatically according to its programmed strategy rules.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do I need a VPS?</h3>
          <p>A VPS is not always required, but it is highly recommended for stable 24/5 operation, lower latency, and uninterrupted trading when your personal computer is turned off.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I change risk settings?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Kohinoor EA includes adjustable settings that allow users to customize risk levels and trading preferences based on their own goals and account size.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>What pricing plans are available?</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA is available in flexible plans to suit different needs: Monthly (@currency.FormatFromUsd(99m)), Annual (@currency.FormatFromUsd(299m)), and Lifetime - 4 Years (@currency.FormatFromUsd(799m)).</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you provide support after purchase?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Support is available after purchase for installation guidance, setup assistance, and general product-related questions to help users get started smoothly.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="eyebrow">More common questions</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Broker, deposit, and refund policy</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">These answers cover the most common operational and policy questions buyers ask before making a decision.</p>
        <div class="faq-grid">
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Does it work on all brokers?</h3>
          <p>Kohinoor EA is designed for MT4-compatible broker accounts. Real-world execution can vary based on broker conditions, spreads, execution quality, and account type, so testing on your preferred broker is recommended.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Minimum deposit?</h3>
          <p>The minimum deposit can depend on the broker, the account type, and the user-selected risk settings. You should define a recommended minimum based on your tested operating range before launch.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Refund policy?</h3>
          <p>We aim to provide a high-quality product and professional support. Due to the digital nature of Kohinoor EA and instant file delivery, refunds are generally not available once the product has been delivered. However, if you experience a verified technical issue that prevents activation or normal use, please contact our support team. If the issue cannot be resolved within a reasonable time, a refund or replacement may be considered at our discretion.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="faq-item">
          <h3>Chargeback requests</h3>
          <p>Please contact support before requesting a chargeback so we can assist you promptly.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div><strong>Kohinoor EA</strong></div>
      <div><p>Answers for buyers covering setup, platform support, pricing structure, and post-purchase guidance.</p></div>
    </div>
  </footer>


@code {
  private CurrencyContext currency = CurrencyContext.FromCountryCode("US");

  protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()
  {
    currency = await CurrencyContext.ResolveAsync(Http, LocalStorage);
  }
}
